b'Urusei Yatsura OVA':
b'The adventures of Lum, Ataru, Ten, and all the gang from Tomobiki continue in an assortment of new \xe2\x80\x93 but no less weird \xe2\x80\x93 stories. 

Watch as Lum, Ataru, and Shinobu encounter a rabbit-clad youth, enter the Room of Destiny, and get a glimpse into their futures in "Inaba the Dreammaker," or see Ran's plans to use a sherbet cone-producing bird to open a sherbet shop one hot Tokyo summer go terribly awry in \xe2\x80\x9cRaging Sherbet.\xe2\x80\x9d Ataru has yet another bad experience with Lum's cooking in "I Howl at the Moon".
